<item>
            <title>[KAFKA-491] KafkaRequestHandler needs to handle exceptions</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/KAFKA-491</link>
                <project id="12311720" key="KAFKA">Kafka</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;Currently, if apis.handle() throws an exception (e.g., if the broker receives an invalid request), KafkaRequestHandler will die. We need to handle exceptions properly.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
                <environment></environment>
        <key id="12605322">KAFKA-491</key>
